Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Andrei Berezhkov's non-defection
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x8v5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Aug 1983
Was Russian teenager Andrei Berezhkov persuaded to withdraw his pleas for help to defect to the West? This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less